NK006(cha)020:0: 'jam dpal gshin rje kha thun nag po'i sgrub thabs bklag pas don grub ces bya ba bzhugs so //
NK006(cha)020:2: bla ma dang dpal ldan gshin rje'i gshed la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK006(cha)020:3: 'agyur meda chos sku'i dbyings las ma g.yos kyang //
NK006(cha)020:4: gzugs sku 'jam dpal rdo rje'i dkyil 'khor lhar //
NK006(cha)020:5: yongs shar kha thun nag por phyag byas nas //
NK006(cha)020:6: de sgrub cho ga 'jug bde'i khrigs su sdebs //
NK006(cha)020:7: kha thun rdo rje'i dkyil 'khor du dbang thob pa'i rnal 'byor pas /
NK006(cha)020:8: gshin rje sgrub pa la don gsum gyis bstan te /
NK006(cha)020:9: sngon 'gro dngos gzhi rjes dang gsum las /
NK006(cha)020:11: thog mar bsang chu byin gyis rlob pa ni /
NK006(cha)020:12: rang yi dam du gsal ba'i thugs ka nas yi ge ram gcig chad nas /
NK006(cha)020:13: ram las ye shes kyi me byung bas dri chab
NK006(cha)020:14: kyi dngos po dang mtshan mar 'dzin pa'i mi gtsang
NK006(cha)020:15: ba thams cad bsregs par bsam /
NK006(cha)020:16: yam zhes pas thugs ka nas yi ge yam gcig
NK006(cha)020:17: chad pas yam de las ye shes kyi rlung byung
NK006(cha)020:18: bas / dri chab kyi dngos po dang mtshan mar
NK006(cha)020:19: 'dzin pa mi gtsang ba thams cad gtor bar bsam
NK006(cha)020:20: bas / / kham zhes pas thugs ka nas kham
NK006(cha)020:21: gcig chad pas kham de las ye shes kyi chu
NK006(cha)020:22: bas / / byung bas / dri chab kyi dngos
NK006(cha)020:23: po dang mtshan mar 'dzin pa'i mi gtsang ba thams
NK006(cha)020:25: a tsan+d+ra man+da la swa b+h+aa wa zhes brjod pas /
NK006(cha)020:26: dri chab kyi snod de zla ba'i dkyil 'khor kha yar la blta ba gcig tu gyur par bsam /
NK006(cha)020:27: bcud yi ge a dkar po zhig tu gyur par bsam /
NK006(cha)020:29: ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai sarba dra b+y+aam shwa d+ha na ya h'u h+r+aihth+aa /
NK006(cha)020:30: zhes bzlas pas sngags de las 'od 'phros pas a la phog /
NK006(cha)020:31: de las 'od 'phros pas sangs rgyas dang byang chub
NK006(cha)020:32: sems dpa' thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs la mnyes
NK006(cha)020:35: sems can gyi lus ngag yid gsum gyi sgrib pa sbyangs /
NK006(cha)020:37: a 'od du zhu nas rdo rje'i chu rdul phra rab tsam par gyur nas /
NK006(cha)020:38: sngo lcigs lcigs 'dug pas zla ba'i dkyil 'khor khengs par bsam /
NK006(cha)020:39: r+ts+wa ku sha'i pir bcug la /
NK006(cha)020:40: r+aa sa ya na ta na gu h+ya sid+d+hi sa ma ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK006(cha)020:41: zhes brgya rtsa brgyad bzlas la /
NK006(cha)020:42: de nas dri de bgegs dang log 'dren la gtor bas mtshams bcad /
NK006(cha)020:43: mchod rdzas dang yo byad la gtor bas nyes skyon dag /
NK006(cha)020:44: mched dang lcam dral la gtor bas thugs dam bskang bar bsam mo //
NK006(cha)020:47: brgyud pa'i rtsa ba bla ma rje //
NK006(cha)020:48: dngos grub 'byung ba'i yi dam lha //
NK006(cha)020:49: legs byin rlob pa'i mkha' 'gro ma //
NK006(cha)020:50: rtsa ba gsum la skyabs su mchi //
NK006(cha)020:52: khams gsum 'khor ba'i sems can rnams //
NK006(cha)020:53: sdug bsngal 'dam las drang ba'i blos //
NK006(cha)020:54: bskyed dang rdzogs pa'i rim pa la //
NK006(cha)020:55: bdag gis ji srid gnas par bgyi //
NK006(cha)020:56: de nas gzhi bdag la gtor ma byin la /
NK006(cha)020:58: de nas bgegs la bka' bsgo ba ni /
NK006(cha)020:59: rang thal mal pa'i snying gar ram las nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor /
NK006(cha)020:60: de yi steng du h'u mthing nag /
NK006(cha)020:63: many+dzu sh+r+ai a kro te ka ya m+aan+ta ka h'u phata /
NK006(cha)020:65: bdag nyid las kyi he ru ka zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
NK006(cha)020:67: g.yon sdigs mdzub dang rgyu zhags can /
NK006(cha)020:68: dur khrod kyi chas brgyad kyis brgyan pa /
NK006(cha)020:69: ba spu'i bu ga thams cad kyang ye shes kyi khro chung tshon gang bas gtams par bsgom la /
NK006(cha)020:72: gsang sngags don la mi mos shing //
NK006(cha)020:73: theg pa mchog la mi dad pa //
NK006(cha)020:75: so so rang rang gnas su dengs //
NK006(cha)020:77: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor la gnas pa'i //
NK006(cha)020:78: khro bo'i ming ni gshin rje'i gshed //
NK006(cha)020:79: de mthong nas ni khro bo gzhan //
NK006(cha)020:80: thams cad kun gyi lag cha 'chor //
NK006(cha)020:81: nga ni khro bo'i rgyal po ste //
NK006(cha)020:82: thugs las byung ba'i khro bo yis //
NK006(cha)020:83: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten khams bkang nas //
NK006(cha)020:84: bgegs rnams ma lus tshar bcad do //
NK006(cha)020:85: sh+r+ai pa ra yak+sha gu h+ya badz+ra ta ki ni
NK006(cha)020:86: k+aa la r+au pa n+ri m+aa ra na h'u phata
NK006(cha)020:87: / skabs 'dir spros pa la dga' na /
NK006(cha)020:89: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor la gnas pa'i //
NK006(cha)020:92: steng nas rdo rje'i thog chen 'bebs //
NK006(cha)020:93: phyogs nas bskal pa'i me dpung 'bar //
NK006(cha)020:94: mtshams nas rdo rje'i tsh+wa tsh+wa 'phro //
NK006(cha)020:98: a kro te ka k+aa la r+au pa ru lu h'u dzah ch+gee mo m+aa ra ya nan /
NK006(cha)020:99: h+r+aihsh+ti bi kri t+aa na na m+aa ra ya tsakra a pa na ya h'u h'u phata phata /
NK006(cha)020:101: bdag gi ba spu'i bu ga'i khro bo dang /
NK006(cha)020:102: shangs kyi rlung sgrom nas khro bo'i sprul pa snga
NK006(cha)020:103: ma lta bu grangs med pa phyogs bcu 'phros pas
NK006(cha)020:104: / de dag na gnas pa'i bgegs phyogs bcur bskrad cing rdul du brlag par bsgom mo //
NK006(cha)020:105: de nas gsum pa rgyas gdab pa'i mtshams ni /
NK006(cha)020:106: 'og min chos rgyal lha yi pho brang du //
NK006(cha)020:107: ting 'dzin mchog la deng 'dir bdag 'jug gis //
NK006(cha)020:108: bla med mchog gi go 'phang ma thob par //
NK006(cha)020:109: lha srin sde brgyad 'byung po'i dpon sna rnams //
NK006(cha)020:110: mtshams 'di tshun chad su yang ma 'da' zhig /
NK006(cha)020:111: bi shwa kro d+ha dz+wa la man+da la h'u /
NK006(cha)020:113: phyi snod kyi 'jig rten gshin rje'i gzhal yas khang /
NK006(cha)020:114: nang bcud kyi sems can gshin rje gshed yab yum du bsgom mo //
NK006(cha)020:115: bzhi pa de nas be con gyi mtshams ni /
NK006(cha)020:119: g+h+ri h+na pa ya g+h+ri h+na pa ya h'u /
NK006(cha)020:121: b+ha ga w+aan bid+ya r+aa dza ya h'u phata /
NK006(cha)020:123: rang gi ba spu'i bu ga nas khro bo snga
NK006(cha)020:124: ma lta bu grangs med pa phyogs bcur spros pas
NK006(cha)020:125: / thun mong du bde bar gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs dam gyi rgyud bskul /
NK006(cha)020:127: khyad par du gdug pa can tshar bcad nas /
NK006(cha)020:130: khro bo de dag bdag gi ba spu'i khro bo la thim /
NK006(cha)020:131: mtshon cha be con rnams bdag gi mdun na 'od lhag ge 'dug par bsgom la /
NK006(cha)020:133: nga yi dkyil 'khor brtan bya'i phyir //
NK006(cha)020:134: khro rgyal byin rlabs las byung ba'i //
NK006(cha)020:135: mtshon cha'i rgyal po be con 'bar //
NK006(cha)020:136: dkyil 'khor rim pa tshul bzhin bsrung //
NK006(cha)020:137: steng yang be con bla bre la //
NK006(cha)020:139: phyogs mtshams be con 'bar bas gtams //
NK006(cha)020:140: be con mtshams las bgegs ma 'da' //
NK006(cha)020:141: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta kro d+ha bi dza ya h'u phata /
NK006(cha)020:143: be con rnams phyogs bcur 'phros shing 'khrigs pas be
NK006(cha)020:144: con gyi gur dang bla bre dang sa gzhir gyur
NK006(cha)020:145: te bgegs dang log 'dren lta ci smos te /
NK006(cha)020:146: srid pa'i rlung gis kyang mi thar bar bsgom mo //
NK006(cha)020:147: de nas rgyas par byed na skabs 'dir mtshon cha rol pa'i mtshams ni /
NK006(cha)020:149: nga yi dkyil 'khor brtan bya'i phyir //
NK006(cha)020:150: khro rgyal byin rlabs las byung ba'i //
NK006(cha)020:151: mtshon cha rnam pa sna tshogs kyis //
NK006(cha)020:152: dkyil 'khor rim pa tshul bzhin bsrung //
NK006(cha)020:153: steng yang rdo rje'i bla bre la //
NK006(cha)020:155: phyogs mtshams rdo rje 'bar bas gtams //
NK006(cha)020:156: rdo rje'i mtshams las bgegs ma 'da' //
NK006(cha)020:157: h'u badz+ra dz+wa la a na larka h'u /
NK006(cha)020:159: nga yi dkyil 'khor brtan bya'i phyir //
NK006(cha)020:160: khro rgyal byin rlabs las byung ba'i //
NK006(cha)020:162: dkyil 'khor rim pa tshul bzhin bsrung //
NK006(cha)020:163: steng yang 'khor lo'i bla bre la //
NK006(cha)020:167: tsakra dz+wa la a na larka h'u /
NK006(cha)020:169: nga yi dkyil 'khor brtan bya'i phyir //
NK006(cha)020:170: khro rgyal byin rlabs las byung ba'i //
NK006(cha)020:171: mtshon cha'i rgyal po dbyug tho 'bar //
NK006(cha)020:172: dkyil 'khor rim pa tshul bzhin bsrung //
NK006(cha)020:173: steng yang dbyug tho'i bla bre la //
NK006(cha)020:175: phyogs mtshams dbyug tho 'bar bas gtams //
NK006(cha)020:176: dbyug tho'i mtshams las bgegs ma 'da' //
NK006(cha)020:177: t+r+aam rat+na dz+wa la a na larka h'u /
NK006(cha)020:179: nga yi dkyil 'khor brtan bya'i phyir //
NK006(cha)020:180: khro rgyal byin rlabs las byung ba'i //
NK006(cha)020:181: mtshon cha'i rgyal po dgra s+t+wa 'bar //
NK006(cha)020:182: dkyil 'khor rim pa tshul bzhin bsrung //
NK006(cha)020:183: steng yang dgra s+t+wa'i bla bre la //
NK006(cha)020:185: phyogs mtshams dgra s+t+wa 'bar bas gtams //
NK006(cha)020:186: dgra s+t+wa'i mtshams las bgegs ma 'da' //
NK006(cha)020:187: h+r+aihpad+ma dz+wa la a na larka h'u /
NK006(cha)020:189: nga yi dkyil 'khor brtan bya'i phyir //
NK006(cha)020:190: khro rgyal byin rlabs las byung ba'i //
NK006(cha)020:191: mtshon cha'i rgyal po ral gri 'bar //
NK006(cha)020:192: dkyil 'khor rim pa tshul bzhin bsrung //
NK006(cha)020:193: steng yang ral gri'i bla bre la //
NK006(cha)020:195: phyogs mtshams ral gri 'bar bas gtams //
NK006(cha)020:196: ral gri'i mtshams las bgegs ma 'da' //
NK006(cha)020:197: h+aa karma dz+wa la a na larka h'u /
NK006(cha)020:198: zhes mtshon cha'i mtshams gsal gdab cing bsgom mo //
NK006(cha)020:200: mdun du ma las nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du ram gcig bsam /
NK006(cha)020:210: mdun gyi ram las me ri dang me dpung 'bar bas 'og me'i sa gzhi /
NK006(cha)020:211: logs me'i ra ba dang d+r+wa ba /
NK006(cha)020:212: steng me'i gur dang bla bre /
NK006(cha)020:213: bskal pa'i me ri chen po tshag tshag tshom tshom /
NK006(cha)020:214: 'ur 'ur gyi sgra dang bcas pa bsgom mo //
NK006(cha)020:217: phyogs mtshams kun tu rdo rje'i me //
NK006(cha)020:218: rnam par 'phro ba rnams bsam ste //
NK006(cha)020:219: ma rung pa dag tshig bsam na //
NK006(cha)020:220: bgegs rnams ma lus brlag par 'gyur //
NK006(cha)020:221: badz+ra dz+wa la ram zhes brjod pas phyi rol rdo rje'i me'i 'od kyis 'khrigs par bsgom mo //
NK006(cha)020:224: rdo rje ri rab lhun po 'bar ba'i rtsibs brgyad na //
NK006(cha)020:225: 'bar ba'i lha brgyad bsnol ba'i gdan steng na //
NK006(cha)020:226: shin tu mi bzad gtum chen ha la'i sku //
NK006(cha)020:227: gshin rje ma tram ro yi dbyug pa 'phyar //
NK006(cha)020:228: gang la cis 'dul tsit+ta'i phreng bas brgyan //
NK006(cha)020:229: phra men dgu khri ma yi 'khor gyis bskor //
NK006(cha)020:230: bskal pa'i me ri smug nag 'bar bas rab tu gtams //
NK006(cha)020:231: me yi 'khor lo rab tu 'bar ba la //
NK006(cha)020:232: rdo rje rgya gram 'bar ba'i me gtor bas //
NK006(cha)020:233: steng gi me lce 'bar ba 'og tu 'phros //
NK006(cha)020:234: 'og gi mi lce 'bar ba steng du 'phros //
NK006(cha)020:235: me ri dgon pa dag ni phyogs mtshams nas //
NK006(cha)020:236: dur khrod mtshan ma'i me ni smug cing nag /
NK006(cha)020:237: zhe sdang 'joms pa'i me ni mthing nag 'bar //
NK006(cha)020:238: gti mug 'joms pa'i me ni smug nag 'bar //
NK006(cha)020:239: nga rgyal 'joms pa'i me ni ser nag 'bar //
NK006(cha)020:240: 'dod chags 'joms pa'i me ni dmar nag 'bar //
NK006(cha)020:241: phrag dog 'joms pa'i me ni ljang nag 'bar //
NK006(cha)020:242: dbang drag gdug rtsub me ni kham nag 'bar //
NK006(cha)020:243: dur khrod me yi mtshams las gang 'da' ba //
NK006(cha)020:244: rdul cha phra mo bzhin du brlag par mdzod //
NK006(cha)020:252: zhes brjod pas mes 'khrigs par bsgoms te mtshams bcad pa'o //
NK006(cha)020:253: de nas ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa la dbang ba'i phyir /
NK006(cha)020:254: rgyu bsod nams kyi tshogs bsags shing smin pa'i dbang blang ba ni /
NK006(cha)020:255: badz+ra sa ma ya dzah zhes lan gsum brjod pas /
NK006(cha)020:256: bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal zhi khro'i lha tshogs 'khor
NK006(cha)020:257: dang bcas pa chos sku mtshan ma med pa las
NK006(cha)020:258: 'gro ba'i don du gzugs kyii skur bzhengs te /
NK006(cha)020:259: rang nyid kyi mdun gyi nam mkha' la pad+ma nyi zla'i gdan la bzhugs par bsam la /
NK006(cha)020:262: khams gsum 'khor ba rab stong nas //
NK006(cha)020:263: thams cad dur khrod bdag nyid de //
NK006(cha)020:264: stong gsum stong gi 'jig rten na //
NK006(cha)020:265: phyogs bcu stong gi 'jig rten na //
NK006(cha)020:266: ye shes lnga yi rang bzhin las //
NK006(cha)020:267: phyogs bcu stong gi sgo phyes shig /
NK006(cha)020:268: badz+ra dz+ny+aa na pra be sha ya phata /
NK006(cha)020:271: thams cad ngo bo mnyam nyid sku //
NK006(cha)020:272: bde chen gar dbang sku gsung thugs //
NK006(cha)020:273: mi zad rgyan gyi 'khor lo dang //
NK006(cha)020:274: gshin rje gshed po'i lha tshogs la //
NK006(cha)020:275: brda dang gar gyis mtshon nas kyang //
NK006(cha)020:276: sgo gsum gus pas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK006(cha)020:277: gu h+ya man+da la a ti pu ho /
NK006(cha)020:278: pra t+aits+tsha hoh bdun rnam dag ni /
NK006(cha)020:280: 'jam dpal rdo rje la sogs pa'i //
NK006(cha)020:281: yab yum sras dang bcas pa la //
NK006(cha)020:282: lus ngag yid gsum gus ldan pas //
NK006(cha)020:283: kun nas dang bas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK006(cha)020:284: sangs rgyas zhing du gang basngagasa pa'i //
NK006(cha)020:285: 'jig rten dag na mchog gyur pa'i //
NK006(cha)020:286: rin chen me tog bdug spos sogs //
NK006(cha)020:287: kun nas sprul te mchod par bya //
NK006(cha)020:288: bdag gis sngon chad byas pa'i sdig /
NK006(cha)020:289: kun nas bsags par gyur pa rnams //
NK006(cha)020:290: rang bzhin med kyang yod tshul gyis //
NK006(cha)020:291: rgyal ba rnams kyi spyan sngar bshags //
NK006(cha)020:292: mgon po kun gyi bsod nams dang //
NK006(cha)020:293: dman pa'i dge ba thams cad la //
NK006(cha)020:294: de bzhin mthun pa'i lhag sems kyis //
NK006(cha)020:295: dang bas rjes su yi rang ngo //
NK006(cha)020:296: bde gshegs byang chub mchog brnyes nas //
NK006(cha)020:298: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba la //
NK006(cha)020:299: tshangs pa bzhin du gsol ba 'debs //
NK006(cha)020:300: mya ngan 'da' bzhed de dag la //
NK006(cha)020:301: 'gro kun yun du bde ba'i phyir //
NK006(cha)020:302: ji srid 'khor ba de srid bar //
NK006(cha)020:303: mya ngan mi 'da' bzhugs su gsol //
NK006(cha)020:304: ji srid 'khor ba ma zad bar //
NK006(cha)020:305: bdag gi dge ba'ang de srid du //
NK006(cha)020:306: kun nas zad par mi 'gyur bar //
NK006(cha)020:307: sems can yongs su smin par shog /
NK006(cha)020:308: bdag kyang dus 'di phan chad nas //
NK006(cha)020:309: byang chub snying po'i bar du ni //
NK006(cha)020:311: thugs rjes yongs su bzung bar mdzod //
NK006(cha)020:312: dus 'di nas ni bzung nas ni //
NK006(cha)020:313: mgon po khyed kyi bka' bzhin du //
NK006(cha)020:314: sems can don kun bsgrub lags kyi //
NK006(cha)020:315: byin gyis brlab par mdzad du gsol //
NK006(cha)020:317: ji ltar dus gsum mgon po rnams //
NK006(cha)020:318: byang chub tu ni nges mdzad pa'i //
NK006(cha)020:319: byang chub sems ni bla med mchog /
NK006(cha)020:320: dam pa bdag gis bskyed par bgyi //
NK006(cha)020:321: tshul khrims kyi ni bslab pa dang //
NK006(cha)020:322: dge ba'i chos ni sdud pa dang //
NK006(cha)020:323: sems can don byed tshul khrims gsum //
NK006(cha)020:324: so sor brtan por bzung bar bgyi //
NK006(cha)020:325: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun te //
NK006(cha)020:326: bla na med pa'i dkon mchog gsum //
NK006(cha)020:327: sangs rgyas rnal 'byor las skyes pa'i //
NK006(cha)020:328: sdom pa deng nas brtan por bzung //
NK006(cha)020:329: rdo rje rigs mchog chen po la //
NK006(cha)020:330: rdo rje dril bu'i phyag rgya yang //
NK006(cha)020:331: yang dag nyid du bzung bar bgyi //
NK006(cha)020:332: slob dpon dag kyang bzung bar bgyi //
NK006(cha)020:333: rin chen rigs mchog chen po yi //
NK006(cha)020:334: dam tshig yid du 'ong ba la //
NK006(cha)020:335: nyin re bzhin du dus drug tu //
NK006(cha)020:336: sbyin pa rnam bzhi rtag tu sbyin //
NK006(cha)020:337: byang chub chen po las byung ba'i //
NK006(cha)020:338: pad+ma'i rigs chen dag pa la //
NK006(cha)020:339: phyi nang gsang ba'i theg pa gsum //
NK006(cha)020:340: dam pa'i chos ni ma lus bzung //
NK006(cha)020:341: las kyi rigs mchog chen po la //
NK006(cha)020:342: sdom pa thams cad ldan par ni //
NK006(cha)020:343: yang dag nyid du bzung bar bgyi //
NK006(cha)020:344: mchod pa'i las kyang ci nus bgyi //
NK006(cha)020:345: byang chub sems ni bla na med //
NK006(cha)020:346: dam pa bdag gis bskyed bgyis nas //
NK006(cha)020:347: sems can kun gyi don gyi phyir //
NK006(cha)020:348: bdag gis sdom pa ma lus bzung //
NK006(cha)020:349: ma bsgral ba rnams bsgral bar bgyi //
NK006(cha)020:350: ma grol ba rnams dgrol bar bgyi //
NK006(cha)020:351: dbugs ma phyin rnams dbugs dbyung zhing //
NK006(cha)020:355: bla mas gsungs pa'i sdom pa kun //
NK006(cha)020:356: 'khor bar skyo ba'i yid bzhag nas //
NK006(cha)020:357: nges par legs pa'i don du'ang //
NK006(cha)020:358: dkon mchog gsum la skyabs su mchi //
NK006(cha)020:359: sdig pa thams cad kun tu bshags //
NK006(cha)020:360: dge ba kun la rjes yi rang //
NK006(cha)020:361: sangs rgyas byang chub yid kyis bzung //
NK006(cha)020:362: ji ltar dus gsum mgon po rnams //
NK006(cha)020:363: byang chub tu ni nges mdzad ltar //
NK006(cha)020:364: sems can ma bsgral dpag med rnams //
NK006(cha)020:366: lus dang ngag dang yid kyi las //
NK006(cha)020:367: nyes pa'i las kun bsdam par bya //
NK006(cha)020:368: bag med chang yang spang bar bya //
NK006(cha)020:369: theg pa dman la zhugs mi bya //
NK006(cha)020:370: lha dang lha mo gsang ba sogs //
NK006(cha)020:371: bla mar brnyas par mi bya'o //
NK006(cha)020:372: phyag rgya bzhon pa mtshon cha dang //
NK006(cha)020:374: rig pa 'dzin pa'i sdom pa kun //
NK006(cha)020:375: tshul chen gsang sngags las gsungs pa //
NK006(cha)020:376: mi dge bcu spong la sogs pa //
NK006(cha)020:377: kun nas ma lus bzung bar bgyi //
NK006(cha)020:378: las dang bka' stsal ma lus bgyi //
NK006(cha)020:379: zhes sdom pa bzung bar bya'o //
NK006(cha)020:380: de nas yi dam gyi lha dang mi 'bral bar dam bca' ba ni /
NK006(cha)020:382: nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK006(cha)020:383: bcom ldan 'jam dpal gshin rje yab dang yum //
NK006(cha)020:384: rgyal ba sras bcas srung ma thugs dam can //
NK006(cha)020:385: thugs rje brtse bas bdag la dgongs su gsol //
NK006(cha)020:386: bdag ni mtho ris longs spyod rgyal srid dam //
NK006(cha)020:387: 'dod pa'i longs spyod bsgrub pa ma lags te //
NK006(cha)020:388: 'gro la snying brtse kho nas don brtson pas //
NK006(cha)020:389: ye shes sgrib med khyed kyis gsal ler mkhyen //
NK006(cha)020:390: bdag lus dum bu stong du gtub gyur kyang //
NK006(cha)020:391: yi dam lha khyod mi spangs bsgrub par bya //
NK006(cha)020:392: bskal pa thog ma med pa'i sngon rol nas //
NK006(cha)020:393: rtse gcig dad pa'i sems kyis bsgrubs pa'i lha //
NK006(cha)020:394: 'phags pa'i rgyal po khro rgyal gshin rje'i gshed //
NK006(cha)020:395: gsang ba'i yum mchog badz+ra be ta li //
NK006(cha)020:396: bskal pa bsgrubs kyang khyod kyi zhal ma mthong //
NK006(cha)020:397: zhal bzang rngam pa bdag la bstan du gsol //
NK006(cha)020:398: bdud dang srin po dregs pa glo bur nad //
NK006(cha)020:399: sgyu ma'i lus la bar du gcod gyur na //
NK006(cha)020:400: rig 'dzin tshe yi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK006(cha)020:401: rdo rje gshin rje bdag gi bzung bar bgyi //
NK006(cha)020:410: ya ma'i tshogs kyi dus la bab //
NK006(cha)020:411: khro bo'i rgyal po'i dus la bab //
NK006(cha)020:412: ma mo mkha' 'gro'i dus la bab //
NK006(cha)020:413: byin gyis rlobs pa'i dus la bab //
NK006(cha)020:414: dbang bskur rgyal po'i dus la bab //
NK006(cha)020:415: dngos grub stsol ba'i dus la bab //
NK006(cha)020:416: dgra bgegs 'gugs pa'i dus la bab //
NK006(cha)020:417: ces rnga brdung zhing dril bu gsil /
NK006(cha)020:418: lus ngag yid gsum gyi sdig sgrib dag /
NK006(cha)020:419: lha tshogs rnams 'od du zhu nas bdag la thim /
NK006(cha)020:421: yi dam gyis byin gyis brlabs /
NK006(cha)020:422: srung ma rnams bka' nyan cing gsung sdod /
NK006(cha)020:423: des bdag nus pa dang ldan no //
NK006(cha)020:424: bdag gi lus ngag yid gsum dang /
NK006(cha)020:425: bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal gshin rje'i gshed kyi sku gsung thugs dbyer med du gyur par bsam /
NK006(cha)020:427: ya m+aan+ta ka 'jam dpal gshin rje'i gshed //
NK006(cha)020:428: yab yum sras bcas pho nya g.yog 'khor bcas //
NK006(cha)020:429: g.yang gzhi thod pas brgyan pa'i 'jigs tshogs can //
NK006(cha)020:430: dkyil dang 'khor du bcas pa dgongs su gsol //
NK006(cha)020:431: srid gsum dbyings nas bskyod pa'i yum chen ni //
NK006(cha)020:432: phyi yi ma bdun nam gru chen mo dang //
NK006(cha)020:433: kha kha re ma t+ai yi tshogs rnams dang //
NK006(cha)020:434: rbod gtong len par byed pa'i ma mo dang //
NK006(cha)020:435: ma ltar byams shing sring ltar gdung la sogs //
NK006(cha)020:436: dam rdzas sngags sogs bdud rtsi'i bcu phyung ste //
NK006(cha)020:437: srog gi snying pos gnas 'dir spyan 'dren na //
NK006(cha)020:438: mngon sum 'di ru lha tshogs bzhugs su gsol //
NK006(cha)020:439: bdag ni rdo rje rang byung chen po ste //
NK006(cha)020:440: mi dmigs tshangs pa'i dngos grub stsal lags na //
NK006(cha)020:441: bka' dang gzhung las 'gal ba mthol lo bshags //
NK006(cha)020:442: mthol lo bshags so ye shes lha yi lha //
NK006(cha)020:443: gnong ngo 'gyod do ma sring rgya mtsho'i tshogs //
NK006(cha)020:444: mthol bshags phul na tshangs par stsal du gsol //
NK006(cha)020:445: yi ge brgya pa lan gsum brjod /
NK006(cha)020:446: phyi nang gsang gsum gyi mchod pa byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK006(cha)020:448: rdo rje gshin rje'i lha tshogs mchod pa'i phyir //
NK006(cha)020:449: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa'i dri ma rnams //
NK006(cha)020:450: ye shes me chu rlung gi sbyor ba yis //
NK006(cha)020:451: bsregs dang bkru dang sbyangs pas dag gyur cig /
NK006(cha)020:454: push+pe d+h+au pe +aa lo ke dang ni //
NK006(cha)020:455: gan+d+he la sogs phyi yi mchod pa rnams //
NK006(cha)020:456: dang +aahdang h+aum gi sbyor ba yis //
NK006(cha)020:457: lha rnams mnyes byed mchod par byin gyis rlobs /
NK006(cha)020:466: thabs shes gnyis med lha yi ting 'dzin gyis //
NK006(cha)020:467: gsang ba'i snod mchog b+han+d+ha'i gzhal yas su //
NK006(cha)020:468: yab yum mkha' gsang las byung a mri ta //
NK006(cha)020:469: zag med bdud rtsi chen por byin gyis rlobs //
NK006(cha)020:471: +aahh+aum sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h+aum h+r+aihth+ai /
NK006(cha)020:473: rtsa ba'i khrag chen m+au la rak+ta dang //
NK006(cha)020:474: gsang ba'i khrag chen pad+ma rak+ta dang //
NK006(cha)020:475: khams gsum bsgral ba'i ma h+aa rak+ta rnams //
NK006(cha)020:476: rnal 'byor nang gi mchod par byin gyis rlobs //
NK006(cha)020:478: m+au la rak+ta dz+wa la man+da la h+aum /
NK006(cha)020:479: pad+ma rak+ta dz+wa la man+da la h+aum /
NK006(cha)020:480: ma h+aa rak+ta dz+wa la man+da la h+aum /
NK006(cha)020:482: mkha' mnyam thod pa shes rab snod nang du //
NK006(cha)020:483: thabs kyi rang bzhin sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga //
NK006(cha)020:484: gnyis med zung du 'jug pa'i ba ling+ta //
NK006(cha)020:485: rnam dag bdud rtsi chen po byin gyis rlobs //
NK006(cha)020:486: +aahh+aum ma h+aa ba ling+ta ba la ti gu h+ya sid+d+hi sa ma ye h+aum /
NK006(cha)020:488: shes rab rang bzhin gsang ba'i mu dra ni //
NK006(cha)020:489: bcu drug lang tsho sgeg dang 'dzum bzhad ldan /
NK006(cha)020:490: pad+ma'i ze'u 'brus dga' bzhi'i ye shes bskyed //
NK006(cha)020:491: bde chen mchod pa chen por byin gyis rlobs //
NK006(cha)020:492: ma h+aa mu dra p+au dza +aahh+aum /
NK006(cha)020:495: bcom ldan 'das ya m+aan+ta ka'i lha tshogs thams cad kyis /
NK006(cha)020:496: bdag gi lus ngag yid gsum smin par mdzad du gsol /
NK006(cha)020:498: byin gyis brlab par mdzad du gsol /
NK006(cha)020:499: zhes brjod pas ya m+aan+ta ka'i sku gsung thugs las yi ge +aahh+aum gsum byung ste /
NK006(cha)020:500: bdag gi lus ngag yid gsum gyi sdig sgrib thams cad dag nas /
NK006(cha)020:501: ya m+aan+ta ka'i sku gsung thugs dang bdag gi lus ngag yid gsum dbyer med du gyur te /
NK006(cha)020:502: lha tshogs thams cad bdag la thim pa bsam mo //
NK006(cha)020:503: de rnams ni sngon 'gro'i rim pa'o //
NK006(cha)020:504: dngos gzhi ting 'dzin rnam gsum las /
NK006(cha)020:505: dang po de bzhin nyid kyi ting 'dzin ni /
NK006(cha)020:507: rtog med spros bral chos kyi dbyings //
NK006(cha)020:508: dmigs med mkha' mnyam byang chub sems //
NK006(cha)020:509: dngos po mtshan mar mi dmigs pa'i //
NK006(cha)020:510: chos nyid ngang du dbyer med mnyam //
NK006(cha)020:511: ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra sa ma ti h+aum /
NK006(cha)020:514: chu zla'i dkyil 'khor ji bzhin du //
NK006(cha)020:515: sgyu ma'i sems nyid de dang 'dra //
NK006(cha)020:516: mkha' la 'ja' tshon snang ba yang //
NK006(cha)020:517: nam mkha'i ngang du ro gcig mnyam //
NK006(cha)020:518: d+harma d+h+aa tu dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a hamh rgyu'i ting 'dzin ni /
NK006(cha)020:520: mkha' mnyam dag pa'i dbyings nyid las //
NK006(cha)020:521: ye shes thugs kyi snying po ni //
NK006(cha)020:522: sems nyid nges pa h+aum du gyur //
NK006(cha)020:523: kun 'byung ye shes rgyu ni h+aum /
NK006(cha)020:524: badz+ra tista dz+ny+aa na badz+ra h+aum /
NK006(cha)020:527: rgyud lnga gdod nas dag pa'i phyir //
NK006(cha)020:528: gti mug 'bar ba'i nam mkha' la //
NK006(cha)020:531: zhe sdang 'bar ba'i sa gzhi chags //
NK006(cha)020:533: nga rgyal 'bar ba'i keng rus brtsigs //
NK006(cha)020:536: yam karma rak+ta man+da la h+aum /
NK006(cha)020:537: ram dz+wa la man+da la h+aum /
NK006(cha)020:538: kham ma h+aa man+da la h+aum /
NK006(cha)020:540: ra rak+ta sa mun dz+wa la man+da la h+aum /
NK006(cha)020:541: kem ni ri ti dz+wa la man+da la h+aum /
NK006(cha)020:542: ram dz+wa la man+da la h'u /
NK006(cha)020:545: ram yam kham gis bsregs sbyangs bkrus //
NK006(cha)020:548: sarba ta th+aa ga ra bud+d+ha tsakra gar+b+he lam /
NK006(cha)020:549: pad+ma man+da la a b+hi shiny+tsa /
NK006(cha)020:550: gzugs kyi yul la zhen pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i
NK006(cha)020:551: zhing khams su dag par bya ba'i phyir rten gzhal
NK006(cha)020:554: rin chen dur khrod gzhal yas khang //
NK006(cha)020:555: ye shes chen po gnas chen po //
NK006(cha)020:556: phyi dang nang med chos kyi dbyings //
NK006(cha)020:557: mtha' dang dbus med nam mkha'i dbyings //
NK006(cha)020:558: gru gsum mthing nag 'bar ba la //
NK006(cha)020:559: zla gam dmar po dbang gi tshul //
NK006(cha)020:560: 'khor lo thod pa bzhi dang ldan //
NK006(cha)020:561: lcags mkhar gling chen bcu gsum ste //
NK006(cha)020:562: 'bar ba khrag gi bar khyams la //
NK006(cha)020:563: gru bzhi sgo bzhi logs dang ldan //
NK006(cha)020:564: sbrul gyi rgya gram mtha' bskor te //
NK006(cha)020:565: rdo rje rgya gram thod phreng mdzes //
NK006(cha)020:567: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he badz+ra b+han+d+ha dz+ny+aa na tsakra b+h+r+aum /
NK006(cha)020:570: bde gshegs thugs kyi rang bzhin gyis //
NK006(cha)020:572: bdud dang mu stegs thams cad dang //
NK006(cha)020:573: gnod sbyin srin po gdan du bting //
NK006(cha)020:574: gshin rje pho mo bsnol ba'i steng //
NK006(cha)020:575: ma he glang rgod bardzisa pa'o //
NK006(cha)020:577: ya ma ye ti ra bam /
NK006(cha)020:584: nang 'dzin byed kyi shes pa tshogs brgyad du 'khrul
NK006(cha)020:585: pa chos kyi skur dag par bya ba'i phyir brten
NK006(cha)020:588: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor ma las byung //
NK006(cha)020:589: zla ba'i gdan ni a las byung //
NK006(cha)020:590: pad+ma'i gdan ni pam las byung //
NK006(cha)020:592: ye shes sems dpa' rdo rjer gyur //
NK006(cha)020:594: chos kyi sku mchog gshin rje gshed //
NK006(cha)020:595: sku che yan lag rags pa ste //
NK006(cha)020:596: dug chen ha la'i mdog ltar nag /
NK006(cha)020:597: zhal gsum mthing la phyag drug pa //
NK006(cha)020:598: dbyug tho dgra s+t+wa ral gri g.yas //
NK006(cha)020:599: zhags pa mdung thung b+han dmar g.yon //
NK006(cha)020:600: zhal gdangs mche gtsigs spyan mig 'khrugs //
NK006(cha)020:601: mgo phreng sbrul rigs rnam lnga dang //
NK006(cha)020:602: glang chen zhing dang stag sham gsol //
NK006(cha)020:603: thod skam dbu rgyan nyi zlas mtshan //
NK006(cha)020:604: thal chen rak+ta zhag la sogs //
NK006(cha)020:605: dpal dang dur khrod chas kyis spras //
NK006(cha)020:606: zhabs gzhi brkyang bskum gar stabs kyis //
NK006(cha)020:607: me dpung 'bar ba'i klong na bzhugs //
NK006(cha)020:608: a kro te ka ya m+aan+ta ka ha na ma tha b+hany+tsa h+aum phata /
NK006(cha)020:610: g.yon nas khro mo ro langs ma //
NK006(cha)020:611: 'bar ba'i kha la gzi mdangs che //
NK006(cha)020:612: lus ni me chen 'bar ba la //
NK006(cha)020:613: zhal gcig phyag ni gnyis pa ste //
NK006(cha)020:614: yab la gnyis su med par 'khril //
NK006(cha)020:615: tri shul thod khrag zhal du stob //
NK006(cha)020:616: be ta li rak+sha yak+sha dzahdzah u tsush+ma kro d+ha be ta li h+aum /
NK006(cha)020:618: g.yas nas bskyed pa'i yum chen ni //
NK006(cha)020:619: e ka dz+aa ti ral gcig ma //
NK006(cha)020:620: smug nag spyang mo tsit+ta bsnams //
NK006(cha)020:621: g.yas na bka' sdod sgrol ging mo //
NK006(cha)020:622: don gyi khro mo ro langs ma //
NK006(cha)020:623: sgrol byed e ka dz+aa ti ma //
NK006(cha)020:624: ma ma trag rak+sha e ka dz+wa ti dzah h'u /
NK006(cha)020:625: ye shes thugs kyi sa bon las //
NK006(cha)020:626: 'jigs byed chen po ya las byung //
NK006(cha)020:627: smug nag ral gri sdigs mdzub 'phyar //
NK006(cha)020:628: mngags pa las kyi pho nya ste //
NK006(cha)020:629: ya ma r+aa dza ni dzah h+aum /
NK006(cha)020:630: yab yum gnyis med sbyor ba las //
NK006(cha)020:631: khrag mig ma mo ma las byung //
NK006(cha)020:632: lcags kyu tsit+ta dung mthing ga khrag bzung //
NK006(cha)020:633: mngags pa las kyi pho nya mo //
NK006(cha)020:634: ma ma ru lu ma he b+h+yo h+aum phata /
NK006(cha)020:636: sha za ging dang srin po dang //
NK006(cha)020:637: ging lcam srin mo sha za mo //
NK006(cha)020:638: ma mo khrag 'thung yi dwags tshogs //
NK006(cha)020:639: ro langs dur khrod pho nyar 'khod //
NK006(cha)020:640: badz+ra am gu sha dza dzah sku gsung thugs byin
NK006(cha)020:641: gyis rlob cing ye shes lnga'i dbang bskur ba ni
NK006(cha)020:643: khro bo'i rgyal po gshin rje'i gshed //
NK006(cha)020:644: ye shes lnga dang sku gsung thugs //
NK006(cha)020:645: yon tan phrin las rnam pa lngas //
NK006(cha)020:646: dbang bskur byin gyis rlob pa'o //
NK006(cha)020:647: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta sh+r+ai many+dzu k+aa ya
NK006(cha)020:648: w+aa ka tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham
NK006(cha)020:653: karma kun len hee hoo h+aum phata /
NK006(cha)020:654: de nas gtum chen gyi bstod pa ni /
NK006(cha)020:656: gtum chen dregs pa chen po thams cad 'joms pa'i lha //
NK006(cha)020:657: dbang byed bdud 'dul dur khrod chas kyis brgyan //
NK006(cha)020:658: sgrol byed sku mchog ma mo 'bangs su 'khol //
NK006(cha)020:659: rab brjid gshin rje 'joms la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK006(cha)020:660: nyi ma 'bum bas lhag pa'i 'od stong phyogs bcur /
NK006(cha)020:662: gdug byed mtshon cha mang po bskal pa'i me ltar 'bar //
NK006(cha)020:663: khro rngams gdug pas srid gsum thal bar brlag /
NK006(cha)020:664: 'jigs byed ya ma r+aa dza'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK006(cha)020:665: rdo rje'i sku la klu dbang rab brgyan cing //
NK006(cha)020:666: gcan gzan gdug pa'i lpags rlon na bzar gsol //
NK006(cha)020:667: sha za gdug pa'i tshom bu dbu yi thod du bcing //
NK006(cha)020:668: khro bo'i rgyal po gdong drug phyag drug h+aum sgra zhabs drug can //
NK006(cha)020:669: phata kyis khams gsum gtor mdzad zhal nas h+aum sgra 'byin //
NK006(cha)020:670: brkyang bskum brjid pas gshin rje'i ya ba ti'i snying gar mnan //
NK006(cha)020:671: ljags 'dril tshems kyi bar nas rdo rje'i thog phab pas //
NK006(cha)020:672: 'khor gyi ma mo rnams kyang bran du 'khol //
NK006(cha)020:673: tsham rngams khro bo'i skan sgra brdabs pa yis //
NK006(cha)020:674: 'khor gyi ma mo rnams kyang 'dar lcug lcug /
NK006(cha)020:675: tshangs pa 'khor bcas rdul gyi thig 'dzag cing //
NK006(cha)020:676: lha chen khyab 'jug ma h+aa de wa gnon //
NK006(cha)020:677: phyag na b+han+d+ha rlon pa rab bsnams shing //
NK006(cha)020:678: dngos grub bsgrub cing klad khrag zhal du gsol //
NK006(cha)020:679: khyung dang 'ug pa lta bu'i khra rnams ni //
NK006(cha)020:680: dam las log pa rnams la gtong bar mdzad //
NK006(cha)020:681: rnal 'byor bdag la gdug cing 'gal byed rnams //
NK006(cha)020:682: rab tu chings shig phung bar mdzad du gsol //
NK006(cha)020:683: gshin rje nag po ya ma r+aa dza /
NK006(cha)020:685: gtan gyi lhar yang khyed la gsol 'debs na //
NK006(cha)020:686: dgra bo'i mgo nas chem chem bsnams su gsol //
NK006(cha)020:687: nad gtong srin mo'i tshogs rnams dbang sdud cing //
NK006(cha)020:688: khyung chen sngon po mkha' la lding ba bzhin //
NK006(cha)020:689: thugs kyi sprul pa khye'u chung mang po yis //
NK006(cha)020:690: rnal 'byor bdag la gnod pa'i dgra dang bgegs //
NK006(cha)020:691: yud tsam gyis ni thal ba'i rdul du rlog /
NK006(cha)020:692: 'jigs byed de yi thugs dam dgyes bskul ma //
NK006(cha)020:693: e ka dza ti gu h+ya ral gcig ma /
NK006(cha)020:694: mi pham khro gnyer g.yu yi ral gcig ma //
NK006(cha)020:695: ral pa sprugs pa'i skra gseb re re nas //
NK006(cha)020:696: khro chung zhal gsum phyag drug stong khams khengs par 'gyed //
NK006(cha)020:697: kun kyang mi bzad 'jigs byed lcags kyu can //
NK006(cha)020:698: lcags kyu btab pas dgra bo'i srog rtsa gcod //
NK006(cha)020:699: dam nyams dgra bo dbang du sdus shig thal bar rlogs //
NK006(cha)020:700: ya m+aan+ta ka dzahya ma r+aa dza h+aum /
NK006(cha)020:701: gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na m+aum h'u /
NK006(cha)020:702: byin du ya ma dzah ya ma nan /
NK006(cha)020:703: mu kha le kha thun mugs nan /
NK006(cha)020:704: ya ma kha thun r+aa dza h+aum /
NK006(cha)020:705: sh+r+ai a kro byi r+aa dza h+aum /
NK006(cha)020:706: ham he ro te bag dzah dzahh+aum bam hoh h+aum dzah da ni dbyings nas bzhengs su gsol te /
NK006(cha)020:708: bcom ldan khrag 'thung khro rgyal gshin rje gshed //
NK006(cha)020:709: bzhengs shig chos kyi dbyings nas bzhengs //
NK006(cha)020:710: yum chen e ka dz+aa ti dbyings nas bzhengs //
NK006(cha)020:711: yum chen srin mo mgo 'phyang dbyings nas bzhengs //
NK006(cha)020:712: thugs kyi sras mchog yab yum dbyings nas bzhengs //
NK006(cha)020:713: mthar byed gshin rje'i tshogs rnams dbyings nas bzhengs //
NK006(cha)020:714: sha za srin mo ging gi tshogs rnams dbyings nas bzhengs //
NK006(cha)020:715: ma mo khrag 'thung 'dud kyi tshogs rnams dbyings nas bzhengs //
NK006(cha)020:716: bzhengs shig bzhengs shig chos kyi dbyings nas bzhengs //
NK006(cha)020:717: bskul lo bskul lo sems can don la bskul //

NK006(cha)020:1027: bdag cag rang rig ye shes blo dang ma ldan pas //

NK006(cha)020:1031: bdag cag rang rig ye shes blo dang ma ldan pas //

NK006(cha)020:1034: khros ma srid gsum sgrol ma'i sku la bzod par gsol //
NK006(cha)020:1035: yi ge brgya pa ci nus bzla /
NK006(cha)020:1036: de nas sku'i cha lugs la rgyas par bstod pa ni /
NK006(cha)020:1037: yab cig lha yi rgyal po gshed mdzad lha //
NK006(cha)020:1038: yab cig sku yi cha lugs 'jigs par ston //
NK006(cha)020:1039: gshin rje'i sku ni 'bar ba'i rgyal po ste //
NK006(cha)020:1040: shin tu brjid cing gtum rngams drag shul che //
NK006(cha)020:1041: khyod la bdag gis bstod cing mchod 'bul na //
NK006(cha)020:1042: bdag la khyod kyis yun du grogs mdzod cig /
NK006(cha)020:1043: bdag ni rtag tu khyod la mchod 'bul na //
NK006(cha)020:1044: bdag gi dgra rnams khyod kyis thal bar rlogs //
NK006(cha)020:1045: khyod kyi thugs rje breng breng rtse gcig rgyun ma thung //
NK006(cha)020:1046: khyod ni thugs rje dam pas 'dir gshegs shig /
NK006(cha)020:1047: bcom ldan ya m+aan+ta ka'i sku yi cha lugs ni //
NK006(cha)020:1048: shin tu ngo mtshar gshiin rje dpa' la brjid //
NK006(cha)020:1049: khro rgyal dpa' brjid 'bar bas dgra bgegs 'dul //
NK006(cha)020:1050: yab gcig lha yi rgyal po gshin rje gshed //
NK006(cha)020:1052: gshin rje dpa' brjid dregs pa'i tshul gyis ma mo 'dul //
NK006(cha)020:1053: gshin rje'i gshed kyis yun gyi lha mdzod cig /
NK006(cha)020:1054: 'jam dpal gshin rje 'i gshed ni dregs pa'i brjid dang ldan //
NK006(cha)020:1055: ma mo kun la 'jam dpal dbang bsgyur zhing //
NK006(cha)020:1056: rtag tu lha mchog bdag la grogs mdzod cig /
NK006(cha)020:1057: srin mo sha za stong ni bran du 'khol //
NK006(cha)020:1058: ging chen ging lcam rnams ni pho nyar 'gyed //
NK006(cha)020:1059: klu rgyal pho mo rnams ni sku yi rgyan du byas //
NK006(cha)020:1060: sha za gdug byed rnams ni /
NK006(cha)020:1062: 'jam dpal gshin rje gshed ni gdug pa'i nga ro can //
NK006(cha)020:1063: khro mo yun chen rnams dang bcas te sku ston cig /
NK006(cha)020:1064: 'jam dpal sku yi thugs rjes bdag la dgongs //
NK006(cha)020:1065: bcom ldan gshin rje'i rgyal po sku bskyod cig /
NK006(cha)020:1066: 'jam dpal sku bskyod bdag la grogs mdzod cig /
NK006(cha)020:1067: g.yas nas yum bskyed e ka dz+aa ti ma //
NK006(cha)020:1068: g.yon nas yum bskyed badz+ra be ta li //
NK006(cha)020:1069: gnyis ka'i sku ni dbus kyi gtso dang mthun //
NK006(cha)020:1071: yab gcig 'jam dpal dbu yi rgyan gyi cha lugs ni //
NK006(cha)020:1072: dbu gsum mthing nag zhe sdang 'bar ba'i dbu //
NK006(cha)020:1073: dus gsum sangs rgyas ye shes yiin pa'i phyir //
NK006(cha)020:1074: thod skam thod rlon phreng ba chen po yis //
NK006(cha)020:1075: dbu rgyan mdzes dang se ral kha ru brgyan //
NK006(cha)020:1076: yab gcig 'jam dpal dbu skra'i cha lugs ni //
NK006(cha)020:1077: dbu skra kham nag ral pa srid rtser 'bar //
NK006(cha)020:1078: yab gcig 'jam dpal spyan gyi cha lugs ni //
NK006(cha)020:1079: spyan gsum gzig pas bskal pa'i me dpung 'bar //
NK006(cha)020:1080: las kyi khro gnyer bstan pas shin tu 'bar //
NK006(cha)020:1081: yab cig 'jam dpal snyan gyi cha lugs ni //
NK006(cha)020:1082: snyan nas bskal pa'i 'brug stong ldi ri ri //
NK006(cha)020:1083: yab gcig 'jam dpal shangs kyi cha lugs ni //
NK006(cha)020:1084: bskal pa'i bag chags 'thor byed rlung nag 'tshubs //
NK006(cha)020:1085: yab gcig 'jam dpal zhal gyi cha lugs ni //
NK006(cha)020:1086: nyon mongs bag chags 'khru byed khrag gi rba rlabs 'khyil //
NK006(cha)020:1087: yab gcig 'ja' dpal tshems kyi cha lugs ni //
NK006(cha)020:1088: nyon mongs dug gsum ma lus rtsad nas gcod //
NK006(cha)020:1089: yab gcig 'jam dpal phyag mtshan cha lugs ni //
NK006(cha)020:1090: g.yas kyi dang pos gdug pa 'dul byed zhing dbyug bsnams //
NK006(cha)020:1091: bar mas gcod cing gtub pa'i dgra s+t+wa bsnams //
NK006(cha)020:1092: tha mas nyon mongs sgrol byed ral gri bsnams //
NK006(cha)020:1093: g.yon gyi dang pos gdug pa 'dul byed khro mdzub zhags pa bsnams //
NK006(cha)020:1094: bar mas zhe sdang 'bigs byed mdung thung bsnams //
NK006(cha)020:1095: tha mas thugs rje chags pa'i thod khrag bsnams //

NK006(cha)020:1098: zhabs gnyis dor stabs ma mo khrag 'thung 'dul //
NK006(cha)020:1099: zhabs gnyis brkyang bskum tshul gyis chos kyi dbyings dang sbyor //
NK006(cha)020:1100: yab cig 'jam dpal sku yi rgyan gyi cha lugs ni //
NK006(cha)020:1101: sku stod zhe sdang gnag phyir glang chen ko rlon dang //
NK006(cha)020:1102: zhing lpags stong gi g.yang gzhi sku la gsol //
NK006(cha)020:1103: sku smad gdug pa bsgral phyir stag gi sham thabs dang //
NK006(cha)020:1104: thod skam nyi zlas mtshan pa'i dbu rgyan dang //
NK006(cha)020:1105: thod rlon phreng bas se ral kha ru brgyan //
NK006(cha)020:1106: sbrul nag stong gi gdu bu sked chings dang //
NK006(cha)020:1107: rigs bzhi klu yi gdengs kas dbu la mdzes //
NK006(cha)020:1108: bskal pa'i me ltar 'bar ba'i klong dkyil na //
NK006(cha)020:1109: ma he'i gdan la brkyang bskum tshul du bzhugs //
NK006(cha)020:1110: h+aum dang phata kyi sgra ni 'brug stong ldir //
NK006(cha)020:1111: 'jigs byed rngams pas gdug pa ma lus 'dul //
NK006(cha)020:1112: khro rgyal gshin rje gshed la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK006(cha)020:1113: sdang ba'i dgra bo thal ba'i rdul du rlog /
NK006(cha)020:1114: rtags bstod la sogs pa'ang bya'o //
NK006(cha)020:1116: bshags pa phul la 'dzab la 'jug ste /
NK006(cha)020:1117: bdag ya m+aan+ta ka gsal ba'i thugs kar //
NK006(cha)020:1118: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor mthe bong tsam pa'i dbus na ye shes sems dpa' tshon gang ba /
NK006(cha)020:1119: de yi thugs kar rdo rje nas tsam pa'i lte
NK006(cha)020:1120: ba nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor sran chung tsam pa gcig
NK006(cha)020:1121: gi dbus na h+aum spus bris pa 'dra ba gcig
NK006(cha)020:1122: gi mthar / h+r+aihsh+ti bi kri t+aa na na h+aum phata /
NK006(cha)020:1123: ces pa'i sngags kyis bskor ba /
NK006(cha)020:1124: bdag gi mgrin pa pad+ma 'dab brgyad kyi dbus na
NK006(cha)020:1125: rdo rje rtse lnga pa'i lte bar pad+ma la dmar
NK006(cha)020:1126: po 'dab ma brgyad la k+aa la r+au pa a
NK006(cha)020:1128: bdag ya m+aan+ta ka'i dung khang du zla ba'i dkyil
NK006(cha)020:1129: 'khor mthe bong tsam pa'i dbus na rdo rje nas
NK006(cha)020:1130: tsam pa'i lte ba la zla dkyil sran chung tsam
NK006(cha)020:1131: gcig gi dbus su gyi mtha' ma la /
NK006(cha)020:1132: a kro te ka ya m+aan+ta ka ha na ma tha b+hany+tsa h+aum phata /
NK006(cha)020:1133: ces pa'i snying po yi ge bcu bdun pos bskor ba'o //
NK006(cha)020:1134: de yang bzlas pa'i dus su dang po sku gsung thugs kyi yig 'bru rnams gsal bar bsgom /
NK006(cha)020:1135: bar du yi ge rnams 'khor lo gsum gyi rdo
NK006(cha)020:1136: rje'i rtse gsum nas byung zhing gnas gsum du 'khor
NK006(cha)020:1137: zhing thim / de nas 'phro 'du ji ltar 'dod pa bzhin bya'o //

NK006(cha)020:1141: gshin rje'i gshed la bskor ba lan stong byas nas bstod pa ni /

NK006(cha)020:1145: dpa' bar mdzad pa'i dur khrod chas brgyad gsol //

NK006(cha)020:1147: las la 'dzud mdzad dbang drag zhi bar mdzod //

NK006(cha)020:1149: lha srin 'dul mdzad khro gnyer mche ba gtsigs //
NK006(cha)020:1150: chags pa ma spang sbyor yum sku la 'khril //

NK006(cha)020:1152: dgra bgegs 'dul mdzad 'khor rnams pho nyar 'gyed //
NK006(cha)020:1153: thams cad dbang du sdud cing drag sngags brjod //
NK006(cha)020:1154: dpal brjid gshin rje gshed la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK006(cha)020:1155: mchod pa bsdus pa re bya /
NK006(cha)020:1156: de dag ni dngos gzhi'i rim pa'o //
NK006(cha)020:1158: tshogs ni ci 'byor ba'i yo byad bshams /
NK006(cha)020:1159: sum+b+ha'i sngags kyis bgegs bskrad de /
NK006(cha)020:1160: ram yam kham gis sbyang ngo //
NK006(cha)020:1161: 'dod yon du byin gyis rlob pa la /
NK006(cha)020:1162: +aahh+aum ba lim ta te dz+wa la lim ta ba la te gu h+ya sa ma ya s+w+aa h+aa /

NK006(cha)020:1174: dgyes ldan lha yi tshogs spyan drang ba'o //
NK006(cha)020:1176: byin rlabs dang ldan pa'i rdzas kyis bsang ba bdud rtsi dang /

NK006(cha)020:1187: h+aum gis chos nyid du sbyangs /

NK006(cha)020:1189: gyis nam mkha' gang bar spel nas byin gyis brlabs pa'o //

NK006(cha)020:1684: bdun brgyud rtsad la khrag zor ya //
NK006(cha)020:1685: snying khrag chod cig tsit+ta nan //
NK006(cha)020:1686: rnam shes phyogs shig na ram ram //
NK006(cha)020:1687: gzugs phung bshig cig su na tri //
NK006(cha)020:1688: yan lag chings shig dza na h+r+aih dug mda' rgyob cig nag po'i tshogs //
NK006(cha)020:1689: dgra bgegs gnyis ka rdul du rlog /
NK006(cha)020:1692: bshal chu +aahh+aum gis byin gyis brlabs /
NK006(cha)020:1694: bcom ldan ya m+aan+ta ka la //
NK006(cha)020:1695: bstan skyong tshogs kyis bskor ba ni //
NK006(cha)020:1696: bdag nyid chen mo rdo rje kun grags ma //
NK006(cha)020:1697: dpal ldan ha ri rdo rje g.ya' ma skyongs //
NK006(cha)020:1698: gangs kyi yum chen rdo rje kun tu bzang //
NK006(cha)020:1699: 'brog chen 'khor 'dul rdo rje bgegs kyi gtso //
NK006(cha)020:1700: bdud mo bzhi yang 'dir gshegs gtor ma longs //
NK006(cha)020:1701: rnal 'byor bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK006(cha)020:1702: sha med gangs dkar rdo rje g.yu sgron ma //
NK006(cha)020:1703: kha rag khyung btsun rdo rje dpal gyi yum //
NK006(cha)020:1704: gser chen mkha' lding rdo rje klu mo dang //
NK006(cha)020:1705: rma ri rab 'byams rdo rje drag mo rtsal //
NK006(cha)020:1706: gnod sbyin bzhi yang 'dir gshegs gtor ma longs //
NK006(cha)020:1707: rnal 'byor bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK006(cha)020:1708: kong btsun de mo rdo rje bod khams skyongs //
NK006(cha)020:1709: btsan la la ro rdo rje sman gcig ma //
NK006(cha)020:1710: g.yu yi dril bu rdo rje zu le ma //
NK006(cha)020:1711: sman btsun khug chos rdo rje g.yar mo bsil //
NK006(cha)020:1712: sman btsun bzhi yang 'dir gshegs gtor ma longs //
NK006(cha)020:1713: rnal 'byor bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK006(cha)020:1714: brtan ma bcu gnyis sman phran 'bum dang bcas //
NK006(cha)020:1715: bran g.yog 'khor bcas gtor ma 'di longs la //
NK006(cha)020:1716: rnal 'byor bdag cag 'khor dang bcas pa yi //
NK006(cha)020:1717: bar chad dgra bgegs nad dang gnod pa'i tshogs //
NK006(cha)020:1718: mi mthun phyogs rnam zhi dang zlog pa dang //
NK006(cha)020:1719: rgyu sbyor rkyen ngan bzlog pa'i phrin las mdzo //
NK006(cha)020:1721: de nas gtor gzhong kha sbub la /
NK006(cha)020:1724: khro bo'i rgyal po gshin rje'i gshed //
NK006(cha)020:1725: ma lus zil gnon bro zhig brdung //
NK006(cha)020:1726: bro brdung gzugs can dgra la brdung //
NK006(cha)020:1727: bro brdung gzugs med bgegs la brdung //
NK006(cha)020:1728: dgra bgegs mgo la chems se chem //
NK006(cha)020:1729: lag pa thal sbyor gyen la sbyor //
NK006(cha)020:1730: 'phags pa rnams kyi thugs dam bskul //
NK006(cha)020:1731: rkang pas bro brdung thur du brdung //
NK006(cha)020:1732: bdud bzhi ma lus zil gyis gnon //
NK006(cha)020:1733: bro ba'i dgra bgegs 'dul ba'i bro //
NK006(cha)020:1734: glu ni tshangs pa dbyangs kyi glu //
NK006(cha)020:1735: tshig 'di don dam rtogs pa'i tshig /
NK006(cha)020:1736: rkang pa g.yas kyis bro brdungs pas //
NK006(cha)020:1737: pho sri thams cad g.yas su mnan //
NK006(cha)020:1738: rkang pa g.yon gyis bro brdungs pas //
NK006(cha)020:1739: mo srin thams cad g.yon du mnan //
NK006(cha)020:1740: g.yas g.yon med pa'i bro brdungs pas //
NK006(cha)020:1741: dgra bgegs thams cad thal bar brlag /
NK006(cha)020:1742: rnal 'byor lus ngag yid gsum la //
NK006(cha)020:1743: gnod par byed pa'i 'byung po kun //
NK006(cha)020:1744: gshin rje gshed po'i ting 'dzin gyis //
NK006(cha)020:1745: ri rab chen po'i rmangs su mnan //
NK006(cha)020:1746: byang chub sems mchog ma skyes bar //
NK006(cha)020:1747: mnan pa yin no ma ldangs shig /
NK006(cha)020:1749: sum b+ha ni brjod pas gtor gzhong ri rab kyi rmangs su dgra bgegs mnan par bsam /
NK006(cha)020:1750: de nas bla ma yi dam la gtang rag gi mchod bstod bsdus pa byed /
NK006(cha)020:1753: yi ge brgya pas lhag chad kha bskang /
NK006(cha)020:1754: rten yod na de la bstim /
NK006(cha)020:1756: badz+ra muhs ye shes pa gshegs /
NK006(cha)020:1757: dam tshig pa bsdu ba ni /
NK006(cha)020:1758: phyi'i gzhal yas khang lha la bsdu /
NK006(cha)020:1759: lha ya ma r+aa dza yab yum gnyis za byed be ta li la /
NK006(cha)020:1760: sbyor yum sgrol yum gnyis kyang gtso bo la /
NK006(cha)020:1761: gtso bo nyid kyang ye shes sems dpa' la /
NK006(cha)020:1762: ye shes sems dpa' rdo rje la /
NK006(cha)020:1763: rdo rje h+aum la bsdus te rim gyis stong pa nyid la blo bzhag go //
NK006(cha)020:1764: rjes skad cig gis lha'i nga rgyal dang ldan pas spyod lam 'jug go //
NK006(cha)020:1766: 'di bsgrubs pa yi dge ba'i rtsa ba 'dis //
NK006(cha)020:1767: pha mas gtso byas rigs drug sems can rnams //
NK006(cha)020:1768: bdud kyi g.yul las rnam par rgyal gyur nas //
NK006(cha)020:1769: rang rig ya m+aan+ta ka mngon gyur shog /
NK006(cha)020:1772: byang chub sems mchog shes rab ting 'dzin gyis //
NK006(cha)020:1773: nyon mongs ngar 'dzin rnam rtog kun spangs te //
NK006(cha)020:1774: ya m+aan+ta ka'i don la rab bsgoms pa'i //
NK006(cha)020:1775: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK006(cha)020:1776: gshin rje'i gshed po skar ltar 'khrugs pa yis //
NK006(cha)020:1777: las kyi gshin rje pho mo kun btul nas //
NK006(cha)020:1778: phrin las drag po'i las la bkod pa'i phyir //
NK006(cha)020:1779: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK006(cha)020:1780: zhi rgyas dbang drag mngon spyod drag po yis //
NK006(cha)020:1781: gnod pa'i dgra bgegs ma lus kun bsgral nas //
NK006(cha)020:1782: bla med byang chub lam la 'god pa'i phyir //
NK006(cha)020:1783: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK006(cha)020:1784: rdo rje gsang mchog gshin rje'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK006(cha)020:1785: 'jigs byed mi bzad gshin rje'i skur bkod pa'i //
NK006(cha)020:1786: dus gsum 'gyur med khro rgyal bgegs kyi gshed //
NK006(cha)020:1787: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK006(cha)020:1788: nyin mtshan med par gshin rje'i gshed bsgoms pas //
NK006(cha)020:1789: gdug pa'i dgra bgegs rdul du brlag pa dang //
NK006(cha)020:1790: bskal pa'i bar du dgra bgegs mi ldang ba'i //
NK006(cha)020:1791: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK006(cha)020:1792: gshin rje sgrub pa'i dkyil 'khor cha na po 'dir //
NK006(cha)020:1793: rdo rje slob dpon mched dang lcam dral gyi //
NK006(cha)020:1794: thugs dam chen po yongs su bskang ba yis //
NK006(cha)020:1795: ya m+aan+ta ka shin tu bkra shis ltar //
NK006(cha)020:1796: sngags 'chang 'khor bcas de bzhin bkra shis shog /
NK006(cha)020:1797: ngan 'gro log par lta ba kun bcom nas //
NK006(cha)020:1798: rnal 'byor rig 'dzin chos rnams dar zhing 'phel //
NK006(cha)020:1799: mthong thos reg pas bde ba mchog brnyes pa'i //
NK006(cha)020:1800: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK006(cha)020:1801: de ltar don gnyis mngon du gyur nas ni //
NK006(cha)020:1802: nyi ltar zhal dro zla ltar 'od gsal zhing //
NK006(cha)020:1803: bdag dang 'gro ba kun la byin che ba'i //
NK006(cha)020:1804: bskal pa'i mthar thug bar du bkra shis shog /
NK006(cha)020:1805: 'jam dpal gshin rje kha thun nag po yi //
NK006(cha)020:1806: las byang don brgyad mngon rtogs pad+ma'i spyan //
NK006(cha)020:1807: mchod rdzas byin rlabs rnams te rtsa ba las //
NK006(cha)020:1808: rang bzos bslad pa spangs nas khrigs su bsdebs //
NK006(cha)020:1809: 'on kyang mkhas grub blo gros ldan rnams la //
NK006(cha)020:1810: 'di 'dra'i cho ga nag 'gros bgyis pa yi //
NK006(cha)020:1811: dgos pa med mod rang dang skal mnyam 'gror //
NK006(cha)020:1812: phan phyir spel 'dis 'jam dpal dang mjal shog /
NK006(cha)020:1813: ces gshin rje kha thun gyi sgrub thabs nag 'gros
NK006(cha)020:1814: su bkod pa 'di ni rigs kyi gcung 'gyur med
NK006(cha)020:1815: bstan 'dzin chos dbang gis rin po che dang po
NK006(cha)020:1816: zho 'khor dang lha rdzas kyi rten bcas gsung gis
NK006(cha)020:1817: bskul ngor 'gyur med rin chen rnam par rgyal bas
NK006(cha)020:1818: spel ba'i yi ge pa ni nor gling pa 'gyur
NK006(cha)020:1819: med bsod nams rab 'phel gyis bgyis pa'o //
